{
  "stem": "945.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But after everybody got out, and we organized ourselves with our belongings, they pointed us to march in a certain direction.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So the people started marching in a direction, and following each other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were surrounded by Romanian Gendarmes with their bayonets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There may have even been some dogs, but we didn't see very much.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was dark.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But later, when the-- when morning started to break, we saw everybody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Do you know the name of that place?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We later-- we didn't know at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we later found out that we were close to the Dniester River bordering Bessarabia and the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this town that we were marched to was called Ataki.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But as we were marching in a certain direction, we started to see in the distance lights.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lights.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Little lights.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know what those lights were, but we were walking in the direction of those lights.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I believe it took about an hour to get to the area.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as we got closer, the lights became more clearer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we still didn't know what kind of lights they were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Finally, we ended up in the middle of a large field crowded with hundreds and hundreds of people, and everybody-- or most everybody-- had a little lantern in front of him.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And those were those lights that we saw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Those people had been there apparently for longer for a day or two, and they brought with them [? premises ?] and lights--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From home.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we realized that they had maybe been a more affluent-- from a more affluent area, or more-- better prepared than we were.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
